data.description: Motivated Seller is open to offers.  Welcome to your dream Florida oasis! This beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a rare find that offers everything you've been searching for in a tropical paradise. Step into a spacious, light-filled living area that seamlessly connects to the kitchen and dining space. This open floor plan is perfect for entertaining and enjoying family time. Whether you're lounging by the pool or taking a refreshing dip, this is the ultimate retreat. The heart of this home is the brand new, state-of-the-art kitchen. Featuring modern design, high-end finishes, and brand new appliances, it's a chef's dream come true.  The roof was completely replaced in 2023. Florida weather can be unpredictable, but you'll be prepared with the built-in storm shutters, adding an extra layer of safety and security to your home.  This Cape Coral gem offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and luxury. Don't miss the opportunity to make this pool home your very own piece of paradise. Contact us today to schedule a viewing!
